CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 19, 2010

[Cite as 10/19/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5069.]

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2009-1580. State v. Hitchcock, Slip Opinion No. 2010-0hio-4980.

Lake App. No. 2008-L-032, 2009-Ohio-4447. Motion for reconsideration granted, and judgment of the court of appeals affirmed. See opinion.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
